ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectBARLEY - 2009 (Feb-July) UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2009-2010 Pool Accounts **
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer the BARLEY unsold from the preceding pool, that began on February 1, 2009 and ended on July 31, 2009 to the current pool period, that began August 1, 2009 and will end January 31, 2010.
